data.oai_dc:dc: North Temperate Lakes LTER: Current Velocity of Lake Wingra (2004)

Profiles of current velocity are measured in Lake Wingra, Dane County, WI, USA at 3 locations. High-frequency data are averaged over at least 30 minutes recording period to obtain the average current velocity.Sampling Frequency: 2 Hz.Number of sites: 3 sites in Lake WingraInstrument: http://www.rdinstruments.com/sen.html - 600 KHz Sentinel Acoustic Doppler Current Profiler from RD instrument
